{"id":35542,"title":"Shapiro syndrome.","abstract":"We report here a case of Shapiro syndrome who presented with episodic generalized sweating, hypotension, and hypothermia. Brain magnetic resonance imaging demonstrated corpus callosum agenesis with colpocephaly. Patient was treated with Clonidine and Propranolol. This case is being reported here because only a few cases of Shapiro Syndrome are reported in world literature.","date":"2014-03-19","categories":"Congenital Hereditary and Neonatal Diseases and Abnormalities","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24640213","annotations":[{"name":"Hypothermia","weight":0.850911,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypothermia"},{"name":"Magnetic resonance imaging","weight":0.826759,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magnetic_resonance_imaging"},{"name":"Medical imaging","weight":0.765178,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_imaging"},{"name":"Brain","weight":0.66182,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brain"},{"name":"Hypotension","weight":0.499656,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypotension"},{"name":"Propranolol","weight":0.369026,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Propranolol"},{"name":"Perspiration","weight":0.327143,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perspiration"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.182524,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Corpus callosum","weight":0.157569,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corpus_callosum"},{"name":"Clonidine","weight":0.127246,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clonidine"},{"name":"Syndrome","weight":0.125733,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syndrome"},{"name":"Literature","weight":0.0623561,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Literature"},{"name":"Resonance","weight":0.0377168,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Resonance"},{"name":"Agenesis of the c